author: Richard Bach
message: The meaning I picked, the one that changed my life: Overcome fear, behold wonder.
title: Thought of the day

author: Plutarch
message: Know how to listen, and you will profit even from those who talk badly.
title: Thought of the day

author: Edmond Rostand
message: A man is not old as long as he is seeking something.
title: Thought of the day

author: Ymber Delecto
message: The time you think you're missing, misses you too.
title: Thought of the day
